      <scopecontent id="aspace_627f5189e295363b513d37f2e66f9ae7">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of newspaper clippings and greetings documenting the inauguration of Benno C. Schmidt, Jr. as president of Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
